        "created_at": "2022-01-20T11:34:07.241Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hi,Experts<br>\nWe want to add a attribute \u201ctrace_format=json\u201d in the configuration file of foundationdb  in the K8S environment. It seems we need to modify the configmap of apple foundationdb  operator.<br>\nWe have designed an operator to invoke apple foundationdb  operator, we don\u2019t want to change apple foundationdb  operator, we want to implement adding the attribute \u201ctrace_format=json\u201d to the configmap by our operator. Is it feasible? Any suggestion? Thanks!</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 3,
